{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-meet-angela-and-basti/task-16","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-learn-meet-angela-and-basti","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Korišćenje <strong><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy</span> + [taifa]</strong> je najčešći način da kažete svoju nacionalnost na španski. To odgovara \"Ja sam + [nacionalnost]\".</p>\n<p>Ovaj izraz se koristi u identifikaciji kao direktan odgovor na pitanje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu nacionalidad?</span>, gde <span class=\"highlighted-text\">nacionalidad</span> znači \"nacija\".</p>\n<p>Za španski, zemlje se ne pišu velikim slovima osim ako nisu na početku rečenice. Takođe mora da odgovara spolu govornika. Na primer:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">Država</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Nacionalnost (Ženski rod)</th>\n<th align=\"center\">Nacionalnost (Muški rod)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"highlighted-text\">México</span></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mexicana</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">mexicano</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Argentina</span></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">argentina</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">argentino</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Perú</span></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">peruana</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">peruano</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Uruguay</span></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">uruguaya</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">uruguayo</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"highlighted-text\">El Salvador</span></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">salvadoreña</span></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">salvadoreño</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Ángela kaže <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy salvadoreña</span>.</p>\n<p>Državljanstvo osobe iz El Salvadora je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">salvadoreño</span> (muški oblik) ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">salvadoreña</span> (ženski oblik).</p>\n<p>Pošto je Ángela žena, koristi ženski oblik nacionalnosti: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">salvadoreña</span>.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-meet-angela-and-basti/task-16"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta je nacionalnost Ángele?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreño</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ova forma je tačna za muškog govornika. Pošto je govornica Ángela (žensko), treba koristiti ženski oblik.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Boliviana</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ángela spominje drugačiji nacionalizam.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreña</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Salvadoreñés</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ángela spominje različite nacionalnosti.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Ángela","position":{"x":50,"y":25,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_spanish_meet_angela_and_basti